Since then, it's been deprecated
in favor of the Google one.

00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:56.000
So I wouldn't use
it if I were you,

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.780
unless you like deprecation
warnings, I guess.

00:00:58.780 --> 00:00:59.722
Weirdo.

